== naming convention ==
run_*.mjs               nodejs executables
web_*.mjs               browser-only modules
web_*.js                browser-only, no exports (".js" prevents import in nodejs)
webworker_*.js          browser-only, Worker() entry point
*.mjs                   cross-platform modules


